‘‘‘设计一个验证用户密码程序，用户只有三次机会输入错误，

不过如果用户输入的内容中包含"*"则不计算在内。’’’
i = 1
password = '123456'
while i <= 3 :
    n = str(input('please enter your pass word with 6 numbers:'))
    if i < 3 and n == password:
        print('password ok,welcome!')
        break
    elif 0<= i <= 3 and '*' not in n:
        print('password wrong,you have',(3-i),'times to try')
        i += 1
    else:
        print('password must have no * included')
else:
    print('opps,no chance again')
